<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Password Reset</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>

</head>

<body style="margin:0; padding:0; background:#F9FAFB; font-family:'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;">

<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="padding:60px 20px;">
<tr>
<td align="center">

<!-- Card -->
<table width="520" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#FFFFFF; border:1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius:12px; overflow:hidden;">

<!-- Top Accent -->
<tr>
<td style="background:#12245B; height:4px;"></td>
</tr>

<!-- Header -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:40px 40px 20px 40px; text-align:center;">

<img src="{{logoUrl}}" width="110" style="margin-bottom:20px;" />

<p style="
margin:0;
font-size:11px;
letter-spacing:0.15em;
text-transform:uppercase;
color:#9CA3AF;
">
Security Request
</p>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Body -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:10px 40px 40px 40px;">

<h2 style="
margin:0 0 16px 0;
font-size:22px;
font-weight:600;
color:#020617;
">
Reset your password
</h2>

<p style="
margin:0 0 24px 0;
font-size:14px;
line-height:1.7;
color:#4B5563;
">
We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to set a new password. This link will expire in 15 minutes for security reasons.
</p>

<!-- CTA Button -->
<table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin:30px 0;">
<tr>
<td align="center">
<a href="{{resetUrl}}" style="
display:inline-block;
padding:12px 24px;
background:#F48120;
color:#FFFFFF;
text-decoration:none;
font-size:14px;
font-weight:500;
border-radius:8px;
">
Reset Password
</a>
</td>
</tr>
</table>

<p style="
margin:0 0 16px 0;
font-size:13px;
color:#6B7280;
">
If the button doesn’t work, copy and paste this link into your browser:
</p>

<p style="
margin:0;
font-size:12px;
word-break:break-all;
color:#3B82F6;
">
{{resetUrl}}
</p>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Divider -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:0 40px;">
<div style="height:1px; background:#E5E7EB;"></div>
</td>
</tr>

<!-- Footer -->
<tr>
<td style="padding:24px 40px 32px 40px;">

<p style="
margin:0 0 10px 0;
font-size:12px;
color:#9CA3AF;
line-height:1.6;
">
If you didn’t request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>

<p style="
margin:0;
font-size:11px;
color:#9CA3AF;
">
© {{year}} Sauti-Cloud. All rights reserved.
</p>

</td>
</tr>

<!-- Bottom Accent -->
<tr>
<td style="background:#F48120; height:3px;"></td>
</tr>

</table>

</td>
</tr>
</table>

</body>
</html>
